                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 847/145.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Obaldia</persName> to
                        President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama, Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-10-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 7, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am deeply grateful for your kind cablegram of congratulations. Throughout my
                    administration it shall be my aim to strengthen the friendly ties which so
                    happily exist between our respective peoples. My greetings and best wishes for
                    your personal and your generous country’s welfare.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Obaldia.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
